name: Silver Snipple S
description: Savor this shimmering, silver S. Splashing yet shining, this glyph is the capital S from the Snipple font by Chank Diesel, a font with the ambition of being both psychedulic and futuristic, now presented here in glistening 3D metallic regalia as it was meant to be, see this S as it sits smiling in the spotlight.
